  "detailed_description": "现实世界已然支离破碎，你会选择在虚拟世界里现世安稳、岁月静好——<br>还是不惜一切地回去，直面现实、放手一搏？<br><br>玩家交流群：615707723（群文件有攻略和角色表情包）<br>新浪微博：唐扬Studio<br>Bilibili：唐扬Studio<br><br><i>如果您是只想游玩卡牌部分的玩家，决定完全跳过AVG部分，可以在游戏标题画面点击\"长明火计划\"图标5次，直接解锁《招式对决》模块全部内容。</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/f97dde860aa4a4139295f85674636e76.webp?t=1761223588\" width=208 height=37 /></span><br><br>期末考试后，军校学生雨人回到家中。和往年一样，迎接他的是朋友、青梅与妹妹。<br>但这一次，一行人其乐融融过暑假的同时，不少异常之事正在暗中发酵。<br>不断重复的怪梦……偶然遇见的神秘少女……边境的偷渡者……日渐紧张的政治氛围……<br>在战争的阴霾之下，寻常与不寻常交织在几个人身边。<br><br>终于，温馨的暑假时光被彻底打碎。<br>迷雾之中的真相、突如其来的战争，一切都来得太过猛烈。<br>七年前究竟都发生过什么？三个国家之间有着怎样的理念差异？战争，到底因何而起？<br>要想知晓这些，就必须行动起来。<br>守墓人，长明火计划，云，实验室……<br>这群年轻人在了解一切真相之后，会做出何种选择；能否成功，又会付出怎样的代价？<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/5c57fd088cca2a8183fde1463ec9a90e.webp?t=1761223588\" width=208 height=37 /></span><br><br>我们只做「对得起自己的作品」，因此《长明火计划》拥有——<br><br>★ 历时7年、15次大修的40万字科幻冒险故事，50位角色共同上演时代群像剧<br>★ 100张CG&BG（不含差分）、150种画面特效与1500段音效共同保障的游玩代入感<br>★ 由闲踏梧桐执导的全角色配音，29位配音演员倾情献声<br>★ 33首风格各异的BGM，绝美女声演唱的OP与ED<br>★ 精心设计的另类卡牌闯关玩法，数十关BOSS战+高难模式充满挑战<br>★ 独立Rougelite地下城模式，300种各异招式带来无限可能性<br>★ 买断制游戏全程无氪金，抽卡只需游戏内金币，尽情抽到爽<br>★ 丰富的附赠内容，《大将军诗集》、番外篇故事等内容更会持续免费更新<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/4d2e02401ee0c5aaad7f6d1cbd10b3bd.webp?t=1761223588\" width=208 height=37 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/d02b835e444b4ae8291f76e3f33cf2cb.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=312 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/96e7fce86a81a230e39b2b5877bb4c86.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=301 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/7d8cf8787f0c56fc13e39fb46396695b.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=329 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/198e6df070a6c009c800abbfd354470e.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=322 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/5c0ce2fa1754a0d52d23ce410d837442.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=371 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/54f425db1f34de13d3750a07ed18147c.avif?t=1761223588\" width=568 height=307 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/965a0b3c7f3350638dd87e13a4ea2b02.avif?t=1761223588\" width=554 height=308 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/383fe120f15a418e0e06e527dc77e33c.webp?t=1761223588\" width=208 height=37 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/18ff6e7cee567ab54dbbae4aaf03f12f.avif?t=1761223588\" width=500 height=1237 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/c3c143821161a20e8f9ff32100dd5a5a.webp?t=1761223588\" width=207 height=37 /></span><br><br>英雄还是懦夫，也许就在一念之间。<br>家国情怀、世间道义、人性光辉，当这些和生死被放在天平两端时，大多数人都会选择后者。但也有人咬咬牙，踏上了舍生取义的不归路。<br>史书不会记载这些默默无闻的英雄，但每个人的心里都有一束长明之火，留给曾经的他们。<br>毕竟，就像无名烈士墓前的大理石上所镌刻的那样——<br>「你的名字无人知晓，你的功绩永世长存。」",
